=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次夢遊都一定搵定幾條安全既逃跑路線<br />\n要走就果斷撤退 成班14年佔過夜佔上癮  <br />\n夠鐘就同班fd去食飯  班差佬谷住仲過癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能過夜</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b1db54f9df86d7dc7a03f319c880af0b68d918b2","tid":1296554,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"If we burn, you burn with us"},{"pid":"e56a42b34be075a640d33c5073bb251ae4601faa","tid":1296554,"uid":24554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"我諗和理非回合啲黑警都咁撚顛，其實都已經係同和理非打左個底<br />\n無論佢勇武定和理非，啲黑警都係睇你唔撚順眼，都係會咁樣打尻你，佢地會容易啲接受到勇武反抗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">(請廣傳！）</span><br />\n<br />\n以下餐廳/店舖係曾經係反送中期間，<br />\n強烈譴責示威者係暴徒擾亂香港、支持黑警濫用暴力、想食兩家茶禮既店舖<br />\n希望大家係抗爭以外，平時都可以齊心抵制呢啲舖頭，唔好再幫襯！<br />\n比佢地知支持黑警係要付出代價<br />\n所有資料由連登、Facebook、IG綜合所得，內容包括但不限於餐廳/飲品店/網店/實體店<br />\n如有補充，可以係下面填表 （spreadsheet唔會公開編輯驚比人玩野）<br />\n會盡量每日更新<br />\n另附上食環舉報熱線 2868 0000或 1823 <br />\n<br />\nenquiries@fehd.gov.hk<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fcomments%2Fcontact_us.html&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=145d907a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/comments/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐黑警/撐送中黑店名單</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI4PSiMK2H2WO9vJtmFd2hdwx0%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=0f6864d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Ak4Hw9c01cfi_RAlMxI